  <h1>Hi Elena ğŸ˜˜</h1>
  <h2>ğŸ‰ 7 Months Together! ğŸ‰</h2>
  <p>Valentineâ€™s Day is almost hereâ€¦ ğŸ’•</p>
  <div id="countdown"></div>
  <p>Will you be my Valentine? ğŸ’–</p>
  <button id="yesBtn" onclick="yes()">YES ğŸ’˜</button>
  <button class="no" id="noBtn">NO ğŸ˜ˆ</button>
  <p style="margin-top:15px;">From: Mark â¤ï¸ To: Elena</p>
